    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="grc">
                    <ab>
                        <lb n="1"/><unclear>Θε</unclear>ίῳ θεσπίσματι
                        <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>κ</abbr><ex>αὶ</ex></expan> δόγματι τῆς Κρητῶν
                        <lb n="3"/>ἐπαρχίας Πετρώνιον
                        <lb n="4"/>Πρόβον, τὸν <expan><abbr>λαμπρ</abbr><ex>ότατον</ex></expan>
                        <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>κ</abbr><ex>αὶ</ex></expan> ἐξοχώτατον
                        <lb n="6"/>ἀπὸ ὑπάτων
                        <lb n="7"/>ἔπαρχον τοῦ πραιτωρίου,
                        <lb n="8"/>τὸν εὐεργέτην καὶ
                        <lb n="9"/>σωτῆρα τοῦ ἔθνους,
                        <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>Φλ</abbr><ex>αούιος</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Φουρσίδ</abbr><ex>ιος</ex></expan> Ἀριστίδης
                        <lb n="11"/>ὁ <expan><abbr>λ</abbr><ex>αμπρότατος</ex></expan> ὑπατικὸς τῆς Κρητῶν
                        <lb n="12"/>ἐπαρχείας ἀνέστησεν.
                    </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <p>Edition based on ICret.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <p>“For divine pronouncement and by decree (of the koinon) of the province of Cretans, (the statue of) Petronius Probus, of clarissimus rank and of eminentissimus rank, former consul, praetorian prefect, benefactor and saviour of the people, Flavius Fursidius Aristides, of clarissimus rank, consular of the province of Cretans has set up.”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="fr">
                <p>“...”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                <p>“Per pronunciamento divino e per decreto (del <foreign>koinon</foreign>) della provincia dei Cretesi, (la statua del) chiarissimo ed eminentissimo Petronio Probo, ex console, prefetto del pretorio, benefattore e salvatore della popolazione, Flavius Fursidius Aristides, il chiarissimo consolare della provincia dei Cretesi ha eretto.”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The inscription was set up when Probus was praetorian prefect for the first time.</p>
            </div>
